  @{b}Development info@{ub}

  
     FBackNG sources were written in C and compiled using SAS/C V6.58.
     FBackNGUI compiled using StormC V3.0.

     Part of file I/O has been coded using standard system library functions.

     Where possible ANSI functions were used. This surely makes it a bit slower.
     This version was developed with portability in mind. The old program had a GUI
     part, which has been rewritten in this one. This also for portability.

                                  
@EndNode

